#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine_distances.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine\\_distances"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances:1 of
msgid "Compute the Haversine distance between samples in X and Y"
msgstr "计算 X 和 Y 中样本之间的 Haversine 距离"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances:3 of
msgid ""
"The Haversine (or great circle) distance is the angular distance between "
"two points on the surface of a sphere. The first distance of each point "
"is assumed to be the latitude, the second is the longitude, given in "
"radians. The dimension of the data must be 2."
msgstr ""
"Haversine（大圆）距离是球面上两点之间的角度距离。每个点的第一个坐标被假定"
"为纬度，第二个为经度，单位为弧度。数据的维度必须为 2。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances:8 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"D(x, y) = 2\\arcsin[\\sqrt{\\sin^2((x1 - y1) / 2)\n"
"                         + \\cos(x1)\\cos(y1)\\sin^2((x2 - y2) / 2)}]\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances:17 of
msgid "**distance**"
msgstr "**距离**"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances:21 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances:22 of
#, python-format
msgid ""
"As the Earth is nearly spherical, the haversine formula provides a good "
"approximation of the distance between two points of the Earth surface, "
"with a less than 1% error on average."
msgstr ""
"由于地球几乎是球形的，Haversine 公式能够很好地近似地球表面两点之间的距离"
"，平均误差小于 1%。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances:27 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics.pairwise.haversine.haversine_distances:28 of
msgid ""
"We want to calculate the distance between the Ezeiza Airport (Buenos "
"Aires, Argentina) and the Charles de Gaulle Airport (Paris, France)"
msgstr ""
"我们希望计算埃塞萨机场（阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯）和戴高乐机场（法国巴黎）"
"之间的距离"

